  "privacyIntro": "At {appName}, your Nzuzo is paramount. This Nzuzo Policy explains how we collect, use, store, and protect your personal and health-related data. By using our services, you agree to the practices described below.",
  "privacySectionDataCollection": "1. Data Collection",
