  "privacyContactBody": "If you have any questions or concerns Maka this Nzuzo Policy or our data practices, please contact us: • EEmail privacy@vitalseker.com • SNkwado support@vitalseker.com • Data Protection Officer: dpo@vitalseker.com • Address: {producer}, Data Protection Office We aim to respond to Niile privacy-related inquiries within 30 days.",
